  <bodyText><![CDATA[<p><img src="/media/13087652/site-masthead-summer-2021-sale.jpg" alt="Summer 2021 sale" /></p>
<h2 style="color: #00533a;">Save £100 per person on all Summer 2021 bookings!</h2>
<p>Italy has now opened their doors to fully vaccinated arrivals from the UK - we can't wait to help you get back to doing the things you love on an extra special summer getaway.</p>
<p>For a limited time only, we're offering you the chance to <a data-udi="umb://document/ed0bcafa85424c78b6325c16c70223f6" href="/{localLink:umb://document/ed0bcafa85424c78b6325c16c70223f6}" title="Lakes &amp; Mountains Late Deals">save £100 per person on all summer holidays</a> departing in October.</p>
<p>What are you waiting for? You deserve a holiday and we're ready to go when you are. It's time to experience more with Inghams.</p>
